summary: For his show in Philadelphia, Harry wore a Gucci suit. The suit features a white cropped jacket with peak lapels and black...
caption:
For his show in Philadelphia, Harry wore a Gucci suit. The suit features a white cropped jacket with peak lapels and black trousers with concealed front fastening, pressed creases, woven side detailing, and flares. He completed the look with a black self-tie neck bow shirt and black leather boots. Photos by pinkraconteur and ohitsthatjen.

Gucci suit
